{"tid":1313004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"音樂普及：介紹鼓棍","createTime":"2019-07-13T15:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T06:48:20.000Z","uid":275735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a78ef62b7b16f4bab246e98e2a31a4ffa7c5ff98","tid":1313004,"uid":275735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"利申先 試過太夜返屋企會係手拎支鼓棍防身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係打鼓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一對鼓棍通常連續係鼓面敲擊上百小時先會裂或者斷<br />\n鼓棍長約40幾cm<br />\n係通利一對80蚊左右唔算太貴<br />\n初學者用5A（比較粗）7A太幼<br />\n而且都係made in usa 或者 japan 質素有保證<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係就千奇唔好用黎打人 好痛架</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有興趣嘅人可以更瞭解鼓棍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHVAr3i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHVAr3i.jpg&h=e3904ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9912edbb89cd9e8513c2ee376e9fee4effe71579","tid":1313004,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"識識樂既男仔好charm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed5129a53c14b7278e14df0cd1a7f670a275958","tid":1313004,"uid":275735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9912edbb89cd9e8513c2ee376e9fee4effe71579","tid":1313004,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"識識樂既男仔好charm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" clas